import React, {
  Fragment,
  Component
} from 'react';
import {
  Helmet
} from 'react-helmet';
import {
  Link
} from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  Button
} from 'materialize-css';
class Register extends Component {
  render() {
    return ( <
      Fragment >
      <
      Helmet > < title > Nimelssa Quiz - Registeration page < /title></Helmet >
      <
      div className = 'row' >
      <
      form className = "col s12"
      autoComplete = "off" >
      <
      div className = "row" >
      <
      div className = "col s12 m4 offset-m4" >
      <
      div className = "card z-depth-4" >
      <
      div className = "card-content black white-text" >
      <
      span className = "card-title" > Login < /span> <
      /div> <
      div className = "card-content  white dark-3" >
      <
      div className = "row" >
      <
      div className = "input-field" >
      <
      i className = "material-icons prefix" > account_circle < /i> <
      input placeholder = "Enter Full Name"
      id = "uid"
      type = "text"
      className = "validate"
      required = "required" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "uid"
      className = "active" > User Name < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      div className = "row" >
      <
      div className = "input-field" >
      <
      i className = "material-icons prefix" > edit < /i> <
      input placeholder = "Enter Matric"
      id = "uid"
      type = "number"
      className = "validate"
      required = "required" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "uid"
      className = "active" > Matric NUmber < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      div className = "row" >
      <
      div className = "input-field" >
      <
      i className = "material-icons prefix" > lock < /i> <
      input placeholder = "Enter Password"
      id = "pass"
      type = "password"
      className = "validate"
      required = "required" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "pass"
      className = "active" > Password < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      div className = "row" >
      <
      div className = "input-field" >
      <
      i className = "material-icons prefix" > lock < /i> <
      input id = "pass"
      type = "password"
      className = "validate"
      required = "required"
      placeholder = "Confirm Password" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "pass"
      className = "active" > Confirm Password < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      div >
      <
      label >
      &
      nbsp; < button className = "waves-effect waves-light btn purple"
      style = {
        {
          width: "100%"
        }
      } > Register < /button> <
      /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      /form> <
      /div> 




      <
      div className = 'row' >
      <
      form className = "col s12"
      autoComplete = "off" >
      <
      div className = 'row' >
      <
      div className = "input-field col s12" >
      <
      i class = "material-icons prefix" > account_circle < /i> <
      input placeholder = "Enter Full Name"
      id = "full_name"
      type = "text"
      className = "validate" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "first_name"
      class = "active" > First Name < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      div className = 'row' >
      <
      div className = "input-field col s12" >
      <
      i class = "material-icons prefix" > edit < /i> <
      input placeholder = "Enter Matric"
      id = "matric_number"
      type = "number"
      className = "validate"
      required = "required" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "matric_number"
      className = "active" > Matric Number < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      div className = 'row' >
      <
      div className = "input-field col s12" >
      <
      i className = "material-icons prefix" > lock < /i> <
      input placeholder = "Enter Password"
      id = "password"
      type = "password"
      className = "validate"
      required = "required" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "password"
      className = "active" > Password < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div>  <
      div className = "inputDiv" > < b > Hover to view password Instruction. < /b> <
      ul className = "input-requirement" >
      <
      li > At least 8 characters long(and not more than than 12 characters) < /li> <
      li > At least 1 numeric character < /li> <
      li > At least 1 Lower Case alphabetical character(a - z) < /li> <
      li > At least 1 Upper Case alphabetical character(A - Z) < /li> <
      li > At least 1 non - alphanumeric symbol(e.g.@ & % ) < /li> <
      /ul> <
      /div> <
      div className = 'row' >
      <
      div className = "input-field col s12" >
      <
      i className = "material-icons prefix" > lock < /i> <
      input placeholder = "Confirm Password"
      id = "confirm-password"
      type = "password"
      className = "validate"
      required = "required" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "confirm-password"
      className = "active" > Confirm Password < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div>  <
      Button className = "btn waves-effect waves-light"
      type = "submit"
      name = "action" > < Link to = "/user/login" > Submit < /Link><i className="material-icons right">send</i >
      <
      /Button> <
      /form> <
      /div>  <
      /Fragment>
    )
  }
}
export default Register;
